[[File:9slideway.jpg|thumb|250px|An underground slidewalk on Metalorn]]
A '''slidewalk''' or '''slideway''' was a form of transportation, essentially a moving sidewalk. They were automated means of transportation on planets such as [[Metalorn/Legends|Metalorn]]. Users stood on the slidewalk and it moved them quickly to a different position. Slidewalks were equipped with automated programs which provided vocal instructions. A slightly more upscale variant of the slidewalk was the [[beltway]], which featured seats on the moving platform. They used [[laminar]] in their construction.

